# GSD Skill Metadata
pack_id: LEARN-101
pack_name: "Learning to Learn — Foundational Knowledge Pack"
version: 1.0.0
release_date: "2026-02-20"

# Status & Classification
status: alpha
classification: specialized
learning_domain: metacognition_and_learning_science

# Content Description
description: |
  Learning to Learn is the meta-pack — the operating system that makes every other pack work better.
  It teaches the science of learning itself: how memory works, why some study strategies fail
  (re-reading, highlighting) and others succeed (retrieval practice, spaced repetition, interleaving),
  how to self-regulate, set goals, and build genuine understanding rather than surface familiarity.
  Every learner benefits from understanding their own cognition. LEARN-101 is the multiplier that
  amplifies mastery across all 34 other packs.

short_description: "Learning science and metacognition: understand how your brain learns and design effective strategies"

